    dc:creator "Arce-Pérez, Roberto; Novelo-Gutiérrez, Rodolfo; Fery, Hans" ;
    dc:date "2021" ;
    dc:title "Cybister (s. str.) poblanus sp. n. from Mexico and notes on other species of Cybistrinae (Coleoptera: Dytiscidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5649606>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5649612>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5649608>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5649602>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5649614> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5649606>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3a–3c. a, b: Part of venter showing ridges on metacoxae (stridulatory organ) and apicoventral angle of metafemora of: (a) Cybister poblanus sp. n.; (b) C. fimbriolatus; c: posterior surface of right mesotarsus of C. fimbriolatus; mesotarsomeres I–IV with two separate series of setae near apical margin: one posterodorsally (on top) and one posteroventrally (on bottom); some further setae removed for better visibility of the setae under consideration." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5649606/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5649612>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5a–5i: Median lobe in lateral view (a, d, g), in ventral view (b, e, h) and paramere (c, f, i) of: (a–c) Cybister fimbriolatus; (d–f) C. occidentalis; (g–i) C. explanatus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5649612/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5649608>
    dc:description "FIGURES 4a–4f: Cybister poblanus sp. n.: a–c: complete aedeagus in (a) ventral view; (b) dorsal view; (c) nearly lateral view; d–e: median lobe in (d) lateral view; (e) ventral view; f: right paramere." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5649608/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5649602>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2a–1c: a, b: Last abdominal ventrite of: (a) Cybister poblanus sp. n.; (b) C. fimbriolatus; c: oblique view on head of Cybister poblanus sp. n.; d–e: last left metatarsomere of male of (d) Megadytes lherminieri (two claws); (e) Cybister poblanus sp. n. (one claw)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5649602/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5649614>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6a–6j: a–f: Median lobe in lateral view (a, d), ventral view (b, e) and paramere (c, f) of (a–c) Megadytes fraternus; (d–f) M. flohri; g–j: median lobe in lateral view (g, i) and ventral view (h, j) of (g, h) M. lherminieri and (i, j) M. magnus. Figures 6g–6j adapted from figs 5 and 6 in Hendrich et al. (2019) (licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution License http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5649614/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

